---
title: Scallops Over Corn Risotto With Heirloom Grape Tomatoes, Thai Basil, and Chili Lime Butter
description: Risotto is generally thought of as a wintry dish, but when you carefully pair it with some bright and bold ingredients, as our chefs have done, you’ve got a recipe for a summery delight. Here, the rice is mixed with fresh corn kernels and Parmesan cheese, then topped with buttery scallops. For contrast, tomatoes, basil, and a spicy lime compound butter are scattered on top, which introduce a flash of brilliant flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b47c4d7ae08b546e417eef2-c8cd117b.jpg
